$committees_
    This package prints the committees who have maximum commits in a given
    org's most popular repositories. [popularity == max number of forks]

    The following are the arguments.
    Organization - Popular repositories for an org.
    Repos        - Maximum number of most popular repositories 
                   for the above.
    committees   - Top committees for all the above mentioned popular repos will 
                   printed as final output.
    
Usage:

    $pip install --editable .
    $committees --help
